title: _SET_BINK_MOVIE_TIME
content:
0x0CB6B3446855B57A// SetBinkMovieTime
void _SET_BINK_MOVIE_TIME(int binkMovie, float progress);Parameters:binkMovie: The movie that is being played.progress: As a percentage (0.0 - 100.0).Seeks a BINK movie to a specified position.Old name:  _SET_BINK_MOVIE_PROGRESSExamples:Lua-- Movie drawn prior
SetBinkMovieTime(1, 50.0) -- Seeks to 50% in.
